Third-party open-source components
===================================

None.

The simulators in this repository are self-contained single-file HTML
documents. They load no fonts, scripts, stylesheets, or other resources
from third-party servers, and bundle no third-party open-source
libraries. Visual design relies on operating-system fonts (Segoe UI,
SF system fonts, Tahoma, Consolas, and similar fallbacks), which are
part of the user's operating system and are not redistributed by
Alin Li OÜ.

Per-simulator notices and SBOMs are published under credits/ and sbom/
in this repository, and mirrored at:

    https://alinli.com/credits/<slug>.html
    https://alinli.com/sbom/<slug>.cdx.json


